So excited to find a coffee place that is a home based business, love the iced latte here, so reasonably priced especially the ice lemon tea. Unexpected but got 2 pieces of cookies to go with the drinks, love the buttery cookies that reminded me of Jennyâ€™s cookies from HK for some reason.

I was running late to pick up the order and they helped me to store in the fridge too ðŸ«¶

Definitely a hidden gem! Will come back for more!

Lovely home based coffee! Taste smooth and delicious:) they have a really cute whippet and owners are friendly and welcoming! Itâ€™s a joy to drop by while walking the dogs to grab a cuppa of caffeine boost.
This is my first time purchasing from them. The iced latte smells just as good as it tastes rich, smooth, and seriously comforting. The owners are friendly!

Love a good cup of Joe? Say no more! Found this (very well) hidden gem while looking for good coffee in the neighborhood. Ordered an iced latte that tasted really good, besting what you might often find from so-called 'specialty' cafes that charge higher. Definitely won me over and will be sure to drop by again next time I'm in the neighborhood.
TL;DR If you're a coffee connoisseur, try their coffee. You won't regret it.

Craving a good cup of coffee and went to visit my neighbour! Brought my own cup too. Perfectly balanced cup of coffee at this price is no brainer. Do drop by and support our friendly neighbour hood batista!
